	<element name="Saddle, Exotic" type="Item" source="Player’s Handbook 2024" id="ID_WOTC_PHB24_ITEM_SADDLE_EXOTIC">
		<description>
			<p>A saddle comes with a bit, a bridle, reins, and any other equipment needed to use the saddle. A Military Saddle gives Advantage on any ability check you make to remain mounted. An Exotic Saddle is required for riding an aquatic or a flying mount.</p>
		</description>
		<setters>
			<set name="category">Mounts &amp; Vehicles</set>
			<set name="cost" currency="gp">60</set>
			<set name="weight" lb="40" excludeEncumbrance="true">40 lb.</set>
		</setters>
	</element> 
